{"id":"314301021_CCZ_equivalence_of_power_functions","abstract":"Let \\(F\\simeq {{\\mathrm{GF}}}(p^n)\\) be a finite field of characteristic p and \\(p_k\\) and \\(p_\\ell \\) be power functions on F defined by \\(p_k(x)=x^k\\) and \\(p_\\ell (x)=x^\\ell \\) respectively. We show, that \\(p_k\\) and \\(p_\\ell \\) are CCZ equivalent, if and only if there exists a positive integer \\(0\\le a< n\\), such that \\(\\ell \\equiv p^a k \\pmod {p^n-1}\\) or \\(k\\ell \\equiv p^a \\pmod {p^n-1}\\).","authors":["Ulrich Dempwolff"],"meta":["March 2018Designs Codes and Cryptography 86(3)","DOI:10.1007/s10623-017-0350-8"],"references":["299476673_Equivalences_of_power_APN_functions_with_power_or_quadratic_APN_functions","238706502_Finite_Permutation_Groups_and_Finite_Simple_Groups","321525420_Theorie_der_endlichen_Gruppen","307875005_A_new_method_to_investigate_the_CCZ-equivalence_between_functions_with_low_differential_uniformity","266993354_Atlas_of_Finite_Simple_Groups","265451880_Endliche_Gruppen_I","264949208_The_maximal_subgroups_of_the_low-dimensional_finite_classical_groups","243017482_Linear_groups_containing_a_Singer_cycle","242922139_Atlas_of_Finite_Groups--Maximal_Subgroups_and_Ordinary_Characters_for_Simple_Groups","226563301_Zur_Theorie_der_Potenzreste","220638788_CCZ-equivalence_of_bent_vectorial_functions_and_related_constructions","220638300_Codes_Bent_Functions_and_Permutations_Suitable_For_DES-like_Cryptosystems","221238566_Some_Theorems_on_Planar_Mappings","221238550_EA_and_CCZ_Equivalence_of_Functions_over_GF2","220638984_On_the_classification_of_APN_functions_up_to_dimension_5"]}